article_title: Grade the Denver Broncos’ performance vs. Indianapolis Colts – The Denver Post
article_text: While some players have been in to work out on their own, first-year strength and conditioning coach Drew Wilson has mainly been preparing for the team’s arrival next week for summer workouts.
